OL,3,C'Maybe there is a change coming': On
OL,4,Cthe ground in Makerfield
OL,6,FAhead of the Makerfield by-election -
OL,7,Fwhich could help determine Britain's
OL,8,Fnext prime minister- ITV News
OL,9,FInvestigations Editor Daniel Hewitt
OL,10,Fspent a few days in the area, speaking
OL,11,Fto those who live and work in this now-
OL,12,Fcrucial constituency
OL,14,FWe met Simon at 4:30am ` the very
OL,15,Fstart of our shift, but towards the
OL,16,Fend of his.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/22
