OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780560333
OL,3,C'Maybe there is a change coming': On
OL,4,Cthe ground in Makerfield
OL,6,FChatting to the people here, it feels
OL,7,Fthey bear the responsibility of their
OL,8,Fdecision heavily.
OL,10,FRarely has so much political power
OL,11,Fbeen held by so few people.
OL,13,FYou can see how much Liam has thought
OL,14,Fabout how to use his vote.
OL,16,FHe is working on a site in Ashton-in-
OL,17,FMakerfield, the most populous town,
OL,18,Fwith Lewis, who runs the scaffolding
OL,19,Fbusiness.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
