PN,31108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780560333
OL,3,C'Maybe there is a change coming': On
OL,4,Cthe ground in Makerfield
OL,6,FFor Liam, it just feels like Andy
OL,7,FBurnham is "using Makerfield" to get
OL,8,Fto "the top job of Number 10".
OL,10,F"Labour for me have just not delivered
OL,11,Fon promises that they made to get into
OL,12,Fpower," he said.
OL,14,FA long-time Tory voter, Liam now says
OL,15,Fhe will vote Reform.
OL,17,FExplaining why, he said: "They've
OL,18,Fcalled themselves Reform to reform
OL,19,FBritain, for me to take Britain back
OL,20,Fhow it used to be. Everybody was happy
OL,21,Fback then."
OL,26,@oD@LOUoD@]O]pD@DOUpD@]O]rD@AOUtD@GO]yD@
OL,26,AZOU}D@KO]
