OL,3,C'Maybe there is a change coming': On
OL,4,Cthe ground in Makerfield
OL,6,FShak moved here from Iraq 25 years ago.
OL,8,FHe says everyone is talking about
OL,9,FBurnham - but he is going to vote
OL,10,FReform.
OL,12,FWhy? Largely because of immigration.
OL,14,FShak tells us he thinks immigration
OL,15,Fhas got higher ` far too much higher `
OL,16,Fthan when he came to the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780560333
OL,3,C'Maybe there is a change coming': On
OL,4,Cthe ground in Makerfield
OL,6,F"Reform said to try and stop loads of
OL,7,Fpeople coming in - because you can't
OL,8,Frent a house now, it's very high
OL,9,Feverything expensive isn't it?," he
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,FHe doesn't dislike Burnham though.
OL,14,F"But I like Andy Burnham as well," he
OL,15,Fconcluded. "Everybody is talking about
OL,16,Fhim."
OL,18,FFor Burnham, this fight is personal.
OL,19,FThere are no Labour posters, just ones
OL,20,Fwith his name and his face.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUvD@bO]wD@LOUxD@EO]
