OL,3,C'Maybe there is a change coming': On
OL,4,Cthe ground in Makerfield
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FReform UK wants to make it all about
OL,12,Fthe party ` and more specifically the
OL,13,Fcurrent government.
OL,15,FThis was a tension ` between a known
OL,16,Flocal politician and new party on the
OL,17,Fblock - you could feel driving round
OL,18,Fthe whole constituency.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
