OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780560333
OL,3,C'Maybe there is a change coming': On
OL,4,Cthe ground in Makerfield
OL,6,FAt line dancing class in the nearby
OL,7,Fformer mining village of Abram, the
OL,8,Freception for Andy Burnham was warmer.
OL,10,F"It (the country) needs a strong prime
OL,11,Fminister," Fran told us. "Stronger
OL,12,Fthan what we've got. I think it needs
OL,13,FAndy Burnham, he's done so much for
OL,14,FGreater Manchester."
OL,16,FWhat about Reform? Fellow dancer
OL,17,FGeorgie was categorical: "No, no, no,
OL,18,Fno, no. I don't like that word. No, I
OL,19,Fwill not be voting Reform. Absolutely
OL,20,Fnot."
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@EpmrD@QpnvD@TO]yD@ZOU|D@EO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780560333
OL,3,C'Maybe there is a change coming': On
OL,4,Cthe ground in Makerfield
OL,6,FUnlike Fran, she thought the by-
OL,7,Felection was a distraction.
OL,9,F"I'm actually a bit annoyed that it's
OL,10,Fhappening at all," Georgie told us.
OL,11,F"It's just taking focus from the
OL,12,FGovernment about what they should
OL,13,Factually be doing. It's like stirring
OL,14,Fa pot."
OL,16,FThe women here talked a lot about the
OL,17,Fcommunity: it's strength and its
OL,18,Fwarmth ` but also the things that
OL,19,Fworried them.
OL,26,@qD@AOUvD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
