OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780560333
OL,3,C'Maybe there is a change coming': On
OL,4,Cthe ground in Makerfield
OL,6,F"I don't go out late night - there are
OL,7,Fa lot of youths causing havoc," Ann,
OL,8,Fwho is a regular at the Wednesday
OL,9,Fclass, said.
OL,11,FBack up in Hindley, beauty salon owner
OL,12,FShannon told us chatting about
OL,13,Fpolitics with clients had become
OL,14,Fdivisive.
OL,16,FThere is a worry, she says, in this
OL,17,Ftight-knit community about saying the
OL,18,Fwrong thing.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31116
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780560333
OL,3,C'Maybe there is a change coming': On
OL,4,Cthe ground in Makerfield
OL,6,F"It's controversial, there's a lot of
OL,7,Fopinions and somewhere like this
OL,8,Fpeople don't know what they can and
OL,9,Fcan't say at the moment," she told us.
OL,11,FSo, what do her customers make of it
OL,12,Fall?
OL,14,FRegular Ethel said she was going to
OL,15,Fvote Labour ` for Burnham.
OL,17,F"I think it's a good idea to get
OL,18,Feverything sorted out now, because I
OL,19,Fthink it's been rough lately," she
OL,20,Fexplained.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@YO]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31117
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780560333
OL,3,C'Maybe there is a change coming': On
OL,4,Cthe ground in Makerfield
OL,6,F"I think we'll probably go for Andy
OL,7,FBurnham. I think he's done a lot for
OL,8,Feveryone. I think he tries."
OL,10,FShannon set up her business three
OL,11,Fyears ago, transforming what once was
OL,12,Fa 1960s sweet shop into her own beauty
OL,13,Fsalon, where she runs events focused
OL,14,Fon building up the local community.
OL,16,FHer grandad Eddie helps look after her
OL,17,Fdaughter while she works. We went to
OL,18,Fmeet him at the end of the day. Unlike
OL,19,Fhis granddaughter, Eddie had strong
OL,20,Fviews on who should win the by-
OL,21,Felection.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31118
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780560333
OL,3,C'Maybe there is a change coming': On
OL,4,Cthe ground in Makerfield
OL,6,F"It's daft isn't it, when you actually
OL,7,Fthink we are letting this people in,
OL,8,Fthen putting them up in accommodation
OL,9,Fand you don't even know anything about
OL,10,Fthem, they're just coming in on a
OL,11,Fboat," he said.
OL,13,FShannon's family has lived in Hindley
OL,14,FGreen for generations. But now, as a
OL,15,Fsingle mother, she worries about what
OL,16,Fthe future could look like for her,
OL,17,Fand her six-year-old daughter.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G18/22
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31119
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780560333
OL,3,C'Maybe there is a change coming': On
OL,4,Cthe ground in Makerfield
OL,6,F"As somebody young with a young child
OL,7,Fit's scary," Shannon said. "You don't
OL,8,Fknow with the way everything is going.
OL,9,FThere isn't a day that goes by when
OL,10,Fsomebody mentions something to do with
OL,11,Fthe cost of living."
OL,13,FShannon hasn't decided - or perhaps
OL,14,Fwon't tell us - who she is voting for.
OL,16,F"My views are very neutral," she joked.
OL,18,FYou can feel her worry about sharing
OL,19,Fan opinion which causes too much of a
OL,20,Fstir.
OL,26,@sD@TO]xD@AOUxD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G19/22
