OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780560333
OL,3,C'Maybe there is a change coming': On
OL,4,Cthe ground in Makerfield
OL,6,FWith Westminster watching, the
OL,7,Fpressure to make the 'right' decision
OL,8,F` about what is broken and how to fix
OL,9,Fit ` feels high.
OL,11,FCertainly, Shannon's decision ` and
OL,12,Fthat of her neighbours on Makerfield's
OL,13,Fbuilding sites, in its nail salons and
OL,14,Fcommunity centres ` is set to shape
OL,15,Fthe future of British politics for
OL,16,Fyears to come.
